5000|$|<b>Linguistic</b> <b>imperialism,</b> or {{language}} imperialism, {{is defined as}} [...] "the transfer of a dominant language to other people". The transfer is essentially a demonstration of power—traditionally, military power but also, in the modern world, economic power—and aspects {{of the dominant culture}} are usually transferred along with the language.|$|E
